divs: sighting detailswhile driving east on hwy 94 about 1\2 mile from 94\894 bypass my fiance pointedout a strobing light in the sky, we watched it while it proceded to turn 180degrees and move opposite direction, while turning it seemed to drop about 15degrees lower in the sky. at the time i thought the object was a helicopteruntil it made the irratic turn. after thinking about it aircraft lights have aconsistant blinking pattern where this had a strobe like pattern. after turningon to 41 north my fiance lost track of it behind buildings that were in the lineof sight, and was not able to locate it after that. if this was truly a ufomany people saw it but since we were headding out of town at the time we wereunable to watch the news that night to see if anything was reported as odd arethere any type of aircraft that lights strobe? we are intrested to find out ifanyone else has reported anything similar.
